#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from the Dirichlet distribution."
msgstr "从狄利克雷分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:3 of
msgid ""
"Draw `size` samples of dimension k from a Dirichlet distribution. A "
"Dirichlet-distributed random variable can be seen as a multivariate "
"generalization of a Beta distribution. Dirichlet pdf is the conjugate "
"prior of a multinomial in Bayesian inference."
msgstr ""
"从狄利克雷分布中抽取大小为 `size`、维度为 k 的样本。狄利克雷分布的"
"随机变量可以看作是 Beta 分布的多变量推广。在贝叶斯推断中，狄利克雷"
"概率密度函数是多项式分布的共轭先验。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:8 of
msgid "Parameter of the distribution (k dimension for sample of dimension k)."
msgstr "分布的参数（对于维度为 k 的样本，其维度为 k）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:11 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  Default is None, in which case a single value is"
" returned."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。"
"默认为 None，此时返回单个值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:15 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:17 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则将张量分配在 GPU 上，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:19 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:22 of
msgid "**samples** -- The drawn samples, of shape (size, alpha.ndim)."
msgstr "**samples** —— 抽取的样本，形状为 (size, alpha.ndim)。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:25 of
msgid "If any value in alpha is less than or equal to zero"
msgstr "如果 alpha 中存在小于或等于零的值"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:28 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:29 of
msgid ""
"X \\approx \\prod_{i=1}^{k}{x^{\\alpha_i-1}_i}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:31 of
msgid ""
"Uses the following property for computation: for each dimension, draw a "
"random sample y_i from a standard gamma generator of shape `alpha_i`, "
"then :math:`X = \\frac{1}{\\sum_{i=1}^k{y_i}} (y_1, \\ldots, y_n)` is "
"Dirichlet distributed."
msgstr ""
"使用以下性质进行计算：对于每一维，从形状为 `alpha_i` 的标准伽马分布中抽取"
"一个随机样本 y_i，然后 :math:`X = \\frac{1}{\\sum_{i=1}^k{y_i}} (y_1, \\"
"ldots, y_n)` 服从狄利克雷分布。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:38 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:39 of
msgid ""
"David McKay, \"Information Theory, Inference and Learning Algorithms,\" "
"chapter 23, http://www.inference.phy.cam.ac.uk/mackay/"
msgstr ""
"David McKay, \"Information Theory, Inference and Learning Algorithms,\" "
"第 23 章, http://www.inference.phy.cam.ac.uk/mackay/"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:42 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Dirichlet distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dirichlet_distribution"
msgstr ""
"Wikipedia, \"狄利克雷分布\", http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dirichlet_"
"distribution"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:46 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.dirichlet.dirichlet:47 of
msgid ""
"Taking an example cited in Wikipedia, this distribution can be used if "
"one wanted to cut strings (each of initial length 1.0) into K pieces with"
" different lengths, where each piece had, on average, a designated "
"average length, but allowing some variation in the relative sizes of the "
"pieces."
msgstr ""
"以 Wikipedia 中引用的例子为例，如果想要将长度为 1.0 的字符串切割成 K 段"
"不同长度的部分，其中每段平均具有指定的平均长度，但允许各段相对大小存在"
"一些变化时，可以使用该分布。"

